elements.name: Validate updates to a Member Event Module

steps.name: I navigate to the SugarCRM QA Website
I login with my username "Admin" and password "Password123"
I select the Member Events Subpanel
I should be able to select the Event Type "End Membership" End Membership
I should be able to select the "No Licensure" Reason
I should be able to select an "09/11/2020" Effective Date
I should be able to select a "John Cleese" Member
I should be able to select the Save button and Save the data

name: Verify Features Added to Member Event Module
